Bobbie Comber https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bobbie_Comber 0 Bobbie Comber (born Edmund Comber; 8 January 1886 – 1 March 1942) was a British comedian, singer and actor. He first appeared on stage in 1904 in Bournemouth. He was born in Bury St Edmunds, Suffolk, England, and died in Bangor, Wales.
